Here is how to make Docker image for dose calc

0. You have to have EGS and BeamNRC installed on your computer.

1. You have to have C25 phase space file in your home dir

2. Put known_hosts in your home dir

3. Make working dir and copy build_image.py and Dockerfile here

4. Run `build_image.py`. Check with docker images

5. Run `docker run -t ubuntu:dxyz`. Should get archive with results in your home dir
